        <description>&lt;img src="https://kaseeia-hsu.github.io/p/test-post/cover.jpg" alt="Featured image of post &#39;Objects of Mundane&#39; Workshop &#39;22" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Exploring Europe with my friends this Summer!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here are some pictures taken from the workshop ‘Objects of the Mundane’ in collaboration with &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://universidadeuropea.com/conocenos/madrid/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Universidad Europea&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://nagami.design/en/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Nagami&lt;/a&gt; in Spain.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s such a great fun to see all the outcomes from these groups! Wishing that we all have the chance to see the final piece that were collected by museum in the future!&lt;/p&gt;
